messages.message:
It will take 2-3 more iterations but how do we feel about this based on what I heard so far:
Current Roadmap:
Auto Refiner – The ability to have Instabase automatically derive extraction criteria with no code
Redactor V2 – Enhanced redaction capabilities for both image and textual data
Advanced Audit – Provide in-depth auditability for fine grained platform usage
High Throughput – Move to near real time processing for large document sets
Automatic Unit Testing – quickly discover what has changed when updating logic or new tooling
Packaged Solutions – W2, Top Bank Statements, Paystub Providers, Passports, and more are out of the box ready
